2024 帖子：这就是周日发生的事情</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/glastonbury-2024-performers-sza-avril-lavigne-shania-twain-credits_-joseph-okpako-wireimage-andy-ford-harry-durrant-getty-images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 2024 表演者 SZA 艾薇儿·拉维尼 仙妮亚·唐恩" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/glastonbury-2024-performers-sza-avril-lavigne-shania-twain-credits_-joseph-okpako-wireimage-andy-ford-harry-durrant-getty-images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/glastonbury-2024-performers-sza-avril-lavigne-shania-twain-credits_-joseph-okpako-wireimage-andy-ford-harry-durrant-getty-images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/glastonbury-2024-performers-sza-avril-lavigne-shania-twain-credits_-joseph-okpako-wireimage-andy-ford-harry-durrant-getty-images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/glastonbury-2024-performers-sza-avril-lavigne-shania-twain-credits_-joseph-okpako-wireimage-andy-ford-harry-durrant-getty-images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/glastonbury-2024-performers-sza-avril-lavigne-shania-twain-credits_-joseph-okpako-wireimage-andy-ford-harry-durrant-getty-images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/glastonbury-2024-performers-sza-avril-lavigne-shania-twain-credits_-joseph-okpako-wireimage-andy-ford-harry-durrant-getty-images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/glastonbury">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐</a>节已落下帷幕——Worthy Farm 音乐节迎来了最后一天，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain)</a> 、加奈儿·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janelle-monae">梦奈 (Janelle Monáe)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">艾薇儿·拉维尼 (Avril Lavigne)</a>等明星都出席了，当然还有头条新闻<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> 。通过下面的新闻回顾了解发生的一切。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年现场博客：周日发生的所有活动</a></strong></li></ul><h2><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paloma-faith-covers-amy-winehouse-triumphant-pyramid-stage-set-3770605">帕洛玛·费丝 (Paloma Faith) 在金字塔舞台上翻唱艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse)</a></h2><p>下午，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paloma-faith">帕洛玛·费思 (Paloma Faith)</a>登上了金字塔舞台，说了句“<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米</a>，我们爱你，你精神饱满地来到这里”，随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paloma-faith-covers-amy-winehouse-triumphant-pyramid-stage-set-3770605">翻唱了艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse) 2007 年的热门单曲《Back To Black》</a> 。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paloma-faith-covers-amy-winehouse-triumphant-pyramid-stage-set-3770605">Blondshell 在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节首次亮相两首新歌</a></h2><p>独立摇滚艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover">兼<em>NME 封面</em>明星</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paloma-faith-covers-amy-winehouse-triumphant-pyramid-stage-set-3770605">Blondshell 在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上首次亮相了两首新歌</a>，其中一首名为“T&amp;A”，音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondshell">萨布丽娜·泰特尔鲍姆 (Sabrina Teitelbaum)</a>告诉观众“这首歌代表乳房和屁股”。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-heres-everything-avril-lavigne-played-3770703">艾薇儿首次在格拉斯顿伯里表演</a></h2><p>艾薇儿涉足音乐界已有 22 年（她的首张专辑《Let Go》于 2022 年发行）。在那段时间里，这位加拿大流行朋克明星从未在格拉斯顿伯里演奏过——直到周日。 </p><figure id="attachment_3770762" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770762" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770762" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Avril-Lavigne-Glasto@2000x1270.jpg" alt="艾薇儿·拉维尼 (Avril Lavigne) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的“Other”舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Avril-Lavigne-Glasto@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Avril-Lavigne-Glasto@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Avril-Lavigne-Glasto@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Avril-Lavigne-Glasto@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Avril-Lavigne-Glasto@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Avril-Lavigne-Glasto@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3770762" class="wp-caption-text">艾薇儿·拉维尼 (Avril Lavigne) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的“Other”舞台上表演。图片来源：Samir Hussein/WireImage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-heres-everything-avril-lavigne-played-3770703">她在“Other Stage”上表演了一场怀旧、热门的演出，</a>卡拉·迪瓦伊 (Cara Delevingne)、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lewis-capaldi">刘易斯·卡帕尔迪 (Lewis Capaldi)</a>和拉米·马利克 (Rami Malek) 等名人都观看了演出。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/avril-lavigne-live-at-glastonbury-2024-setlist-review-photos-3770749">阅读<em>《NME》</em>对艾薇儿·拉维尼 (Avril Lavigne) 格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 演出的三星级评论</a>。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-louis-tomlinson-brings-huge-screen-to-the-festival-just-to-watch-the-euros-3770716">Louis Tomlinson 为 Glasto 带来了电视屏幕，以便他可以观看欧洲杯</a></h2><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/louis-tomlinson">路易斯·汤姆林森 (Louis Tomlinson)</a>将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-louis-tomlinson-brings-huge-screen-to-the-festival-just-to-watch-the-euros-3770716">自己的电视屏幕带到格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury)，这样他就可以观看欧洲杯</a>，并在露营地设置了一个大平板屏幕，其他格拉斯顿伯里观众也加入了他的行列，他们同样兴奋地看到英格兰击败斯洛伐克。这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>员工告诉<em>《卫报》，</em>这显然是他带来的第二块屏幕，因为第一个屏幕“破裂了”。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/social-media-reacts-to-shania-twain-set-at-glastonbury-2024-3770637">仙妮亚·唐恩在“传奇”时段登上金字塔舞台，但在家中观看的观众却遇到了声音问题</a></h2><p>仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 在备受期待的“传奇”节目中登上了金字塔舞台，她以 1997 年的热门歌曲“That Don&#39;t Impress Me Much”拉开了序幕。 </p><figure id="attachment_3770640" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770640" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770640" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270.jpg" alt="仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 于 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节第五天在金字塔舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/shania-twain-glastonbury@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3770640" class="wp-caption-text">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上表演。图片来源：Joe Maher/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/social-media-reacts-to-shania-twain-set-at-glastonbury-2024-3770637">国内观众批评了该剧的声音问题</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/shania-twain-glastonbury-2024-setlist-photos-3770685">阅读<em>NME 对</em>吐温在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上的“高营富矿”的三星级评论</a>。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-heres-what-sza-played-to-close-out-the-show-3770815">尽管技术困难，SZA 在周末最后一场金字塔头条比赛中表现出色</a></h2><p>SZA 为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/szas-headlining-glastonbury-set-plagued-by-technical-difficulties-social-media-reacts-3770821">Glastonbury 2024 带来了一场极具魅力的决赛头条表演</a>，充满了时代和美学的视觉跳跃——但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/szas-headlining-glastonbury-set-plagued-by-technical-difficulties-social-media-reacts-3770821">不幸的是，她的布景也因麦克风和浑浊的声音而受到技术困难的困扰</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sza-live-at-glastonbury-2024-setlist-review-photos-3770784">阅读<em>NME 对</em>SZA 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上的头条新闻的四星评论</a>。</p><h2>伦敦文法学校派出乔治·菲茨杰拉德参加公园舞台决赛</h2><p>距上次在格拉斯顿伯里亮相十年后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/london-grammar">伦敦文法学校</a>重返沃西农场。这支电子流行乐队以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-fitzgerald">乔治·菲茨杰拉德（George Fitzgerald</a> ）的《宝贝就是你》（Baby It&#39;s You）结束了公园舞台，汉娜·里德（Hannah Reid）宣称他们的嘉宾不仅是“音乐界最友善的人，而且是最有才华的人”。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-the-national-perform-mesmerising-set-with-kate-stables-as-a-special-guest-3770858">The National 在 Other Stage 的闭场演出中推出了 This Is The Kit 的 Kate Stables</a></h2><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">国家剧院</a>在 Other Stage 的闭幕演出中为《Rylan》带来了 Kate Stables（又名<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/this-is-the-kit">This Is The Kit）</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3770897" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770897" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770897" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423.jpg" alt="2024 年格拉斯顿伯里国家音乐节现场演出。图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/NME_Glasto24_TheNational_Other_AFord-62423-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="cap