eview-photos-setlist-3770486">四星评价</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">小西姆兹</a>的金字塔表演<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/little-simz-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-stage-setlist-photos-3770489">标志着她成为未来的头条新闻</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/camila-cabello-glastonbury-live-review-setlist-photos-3770276">卡米拉卡贝洛则表现混乱</a>。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-the-last-dinner-party-speak-on-the-general-election-encourage-voters-to-have-some-fucking-empathy-3770181"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> <a class="c-link c-link--focus-visible" href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-stringify-link="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024" data-sk="tooltip_parent">请返回<i data-stringify-type="italic">NME</i> ，了解 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的最新</a>新闻、评论、采访、照片、谣言等。请<a class="c-link c-link--focus-visible" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-stringify-link="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371" data-sk="tooltip_parent">在此处查看<i data-stringify-type="italic">NME</i>直播博客，了解格拉斯顿伯里发生的所有最新动态</a>。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-heres-what-sza-played-to-close-out-the-show-3770815">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节后：以下是 SZA 在结束演出时演奏的曲目，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
